WEBVTT

00:00:30.208 --> 00:00:31.952
That's me behind the wheel,

00:00:31.976 --> 00:00:34.200
with my sister and my best
friend at the time.

00:00:35.875 --> 00:00:37.801
And one day,

00:00:37.825 --> 00:00:40.908
he came home, when I was
about 10 years old,

00:00:40.932 --> 00:00:43.558
and at the dinner table, he announced

00:00:43.582 --> 00:00:47.294
that for our next project, 
we were going to build ...

00:00:47.318 --> 00:00:48.468
a robot.

00:00:49.604 --> 00:00:50.759
A robot.

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.183
Now, I was thrilled about this,

00:00:53.207 --> 00:00:57.009
because at school,
there was a bully named Kevin,

00:00:57.033 --> 00:00:58.922
and he was picking on me,

00:00:58.946 --> 00:01:01.336
because I was the only
Jewish kid in class.